                                "en": "Oh you <clutz>, how could you forget the train tickets at home?"
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Вратарь сыграл как <шляпа> и пропустил очень лёгкий мяч.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "The goalkeeper played like a <bungler> and let in a very easy ball."
